more than enough?

593
00:34:24,540 --> 00:34:25,180
She's the first girl

594
00:34:25,180 --> 00:34:26,460
I truly fancy.

595
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,260
Even if I do encounter

596
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:29,620
