599
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:37,180
You're right.

600
00:34:37,220 --> 00:34:38,780
I actually can't refute your words.

601
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:39,460
Master, what about you?

602
00:34:39,620 --> 00:34:40,540
Do you have a girl you fancy?

603
00:34:40,540 --> 00:34:40,980
I do.

604
00:34:41,060 --> 00:34:41,660
Where is she?

605
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:43,500
All of them are dead.

606
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:45,260
It's because I've lived for too long.

607
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:47,020
That's why all of them are dead.

608
00:34:48,620 --> 00:34:49,180
Wait.

609
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:51,420
Them?

610
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,220
