667
00:38:05,180 --> 00:38:06,100
Yingxian.

668
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,220
You know what?

669
00:38:09,740 --> 00:38:10,820
Now, it feels like

670
00:38:12,220 --> 00:38:13,380
