672
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:18,580
I can see it every day.

673
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,580
It's sharp

674
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:23,660
and scary.

675
00:38:24,540 --> 00:38:25,340
However, I have no idea

676
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:26,580
when it'll land on my head.

677
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,420
I worry

678
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:31,340
and live in fear every day.

679
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:34,580
I can never sleep well.

680
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:43,820
Your Highness, don't be afraid.

681
00:38:45,420 --> 00:38:47,100
I'll always stay by your side

682
00:38:47,490 --> 00:38:48,370
and protect you.

683
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:01,900
- Senior Lei.
- Senior Lei.

684
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:05,980
That's him, right?

685
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:07,060
I think so.

686
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:08,420
Dongba.

687
00:39:10,860 --> 00:39:12,580
In the past, I've heard
about a kind of people

688
00:39:12,740 --> 00:39:14,620
called bookworms.

689
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:16,500
Initially, I was dismissive of them

690
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:18,660
until I got to know Mr. Xie Xuan.

691
00:39:19,940 --> 00:39:22,220
Mr. Xie, what are you reading today?

692
