[Luminous Moon Sword Techniques]

693
00:39:25,540 --> 00:39:26,540
Luminous Moon Sword Techniques.

694
00:39:27,620 --> 00:39:28,540
Are you reading a sword manual?

695
00:39:28,980 --> 00:39:30,380
Second Senior, do you practice
swordsmanship as well?

696
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:34,060
I'm a member of the Lei Clan, you know?

697
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,420
Of course, I don't.

698
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:40,180
But Xinyue

699
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:41,460
is the successor of Heart Sword.

700
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:42,340
Therefore, I heard

701
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:43,460
about the Luminous Moon
Sword Techniques.

702
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:45,580
These are highly advanced
sword techniques

703
00:39:45,580 --> 00:39:46,620
