without practicing it.

706
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:50,100
Can you even master it?

707
00:39:50,420 --> 00:39:51,380
Who said I wasn't practicing it?

708
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:53,940
I'm practicing it in my heart.

709
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:57,180
You think that I'm just reading a book.

710
00:39:57,420 --> 00:39:58,540
However, I practice
each technique in my heart

711
00:39:58,620 --> 00:40:00,580
as I read it.

712
00:40:00,980 --> 00:40:02,060
Once I'm done,

713
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:03,580
I'll master the techniques.

714
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:06,980
Mr. Xie, I never expected you
to be a martial arts expert too.

715
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:09,420
I've never been in a fight.

716
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:12,340
My sect always treats people
with courtesy and respect.

717
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:14,900
Most of our sect members
don't know martial arts.

718
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:15,860
What do you all do

719
