unreasonable people, then?

720
00:40:19,340 --> 00:40:20,100
If so,

721
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:22,020
I'll beat him up
until he regains some senses.

722
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:24,220
But you said you didn't know
